NG0211:3132: thig skor rim pa bzhi ru bskor //
NG0211:3133: dbus su pho brang zlum po la //
NG0211:3134: gdug pa'i gzugs dang yul gyi ming *//
NG0211:3135: ser ba drag tu phob ces bri //
NG0211:3136: zla gam gsum pa ser srung dang *//
NG0211:3137: yul lha'i sbyor ba gzhom pa bri //
NG0211:3138: phyi rim rdo rje rgya gram bri //
NG0211:3139: rtsa ba'i drag sngags 'bru bzhi dgod //
NG0211:3140: yang logs rtsibs chen bcu gnyis la //
NG0211:3141: chu dril zor gyi dbab pa dgod //
NG0211:3142: tha ma'i rtsibs chen bcu drug la //
NG0211:3143: thabs dang drag po gzir ba yis //
NG0211:3144: lo tog gzhom pa'i spu gri dgod /
NG0211:3145: kha sbyor tshon skud brkyang pas sngags //
NG0211:3146: thod chen sbyang sprugs shu+u na du //
NG0211:3147: gcod pa'i 'khor lo tsha ra gzhug / gri khrag
NG0211:3148: khyi khrag rta nag khrag / dod bur sngags bstim
NG0211:3149: zor du 'bar // sngo sna nal khrag dug sna zho //
NG0211:3150: zhabs mar sngags bstim thal gyi rdzas //
NG0211:3151: lcags phur seng ldeng rdzas rgod rnams //
NG0211:3152: dug gi ngar blud drag sngags dkrug / spogs pa drag pos gzir ba'i rdzas //
NG0211:3153: dgun zla gsum la nyin zhag gcig / chu dril khri tsho zhib tu bstim //
NG0211:3154: dpyid zla gsum la zor dril brdeg / zhag re dong du thod par bstim //
NG0211:3155: dbyar zla gsum gyi nya stong la //
NG0211:3156: zhag gsum nya la gta' ma gzhug / yul dbus klu dang lha rten la //
NG0211:3157: thod chen spyang thod sbrul gzhug dang *//
NG0211:3158: ston zla nya stong rnams bzlog brdeg / brgya pa bcu par khrag la bstim //
NG0211:3159: stong gi bar du rdzas rnams bstims /
NG0211:3160: khri bar phur pa dgug rdzas bstim //
NG0211:3161: drag sngags rnal bzlog 'byung ba dkrug / zor dril thab dang gzir las sbyar //
NG0211:3162: de yis thams cad ma lus 'joms //
NG0211:3163: sman dang rtsi shing lo tog la //
NG0211:3164: drag po gnam lcags ser ba 'bebs //
NG0211:3165: tshe brgyad sa sros bzhi yi 'jing *//
NG0211:3166: nya yi srod 'khor bcu gcig yol //
NG0211:3167: nyi cu dgu yi mdung gang la //
NG0211:3168: dbab pa gsum pa'i sbyor ba brtsam //
NG0211:3169: grub na gta' ma gdugs kyi gso //
NG0211:3170: de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis nyid kyi sku
NG0211:3171: gsung thugs rdo rje las drag sngags 'di bton to
NG0211:3173: u kham phrom phrom hri la phob //
NG0211:3174: shar shar hril drag tu phob /
NG0211:3177: ka dum ram phob ka e yam dun na ga snying gzer phrom ya hril shar /
NG0211:3178: chu mig lha rten la dmigs shing *//
NG0211:3179: zor thab sbyor ba thod pa zangs //
NG0211:3180: mi lag mi sog thal 'jim zor //
NG0211:3181: gzugs brnyan gnyis par rten bzhag la //
NG0211:3182: 'byung ba dkrugs la khri bzhi bstim //
NG0211:3183: gar dmigs klu gnas phur pa gdab //
NG0211:3186: rang yang rang la gab par bshad //
NG0211:3188: drag po gnam thog 'phang ba'i sbyor ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0211:3189: de bzhin gnas dang mtshams bcad la //
NG0211:3190: thog rgod gri thog nyams can du //
NG0211:3191: me long gser dang thog lcags zangs //
NG0211:3192: rdo nag yungs kar rgyal po spungs //
NG0211:3193: rta nag rabs chad khyi nag khrag / dug sna dang bcas steng 'og rten //
NG0211:3194: yul dang bcas pa'i ming rus khams //
NG0211:3195: ling+ga rten dang rgya gram dbus //
NG0211:3196: thig skor rtse mo drug pa bri //
NG0211:3197: rgya gram 'bru bzhi sngags kyi lus //
NG0211:3198: thod skor spu gri tshan res dgang *//
NG0211:3199: gser thog gzhu dang spel dang gcag / 'phangs pa bsrung dang gcun la dbab //
NG0211:3201: spos dang bdud rtsis bsangs la bkru //
NG0211:3202: drag sngags 'khor lo bskor la gzhug / dri mda' dug mda' ltas ngan mda' //
NG0211:3203: bcas la gser blugs dgra la 'phang *//
NG0211:3204: nya dang nyi shu dgu la shis //
NG0211:3205: sngags pa zil gnon phyag rgyar gsal //
NG0211:3206: lus la ye shes 'khor lo bca' //
NG0211:3207: 'khor lo bsrung ba'i drag sngags spro //
NG0211:3208: che ba'i nga rgyal drag pos bskul //
NG0211:3209: sngags la ltas ngan tri mda' sbyar //
NG0211:3210: dug mda' thog rgod gcun dang sdeb //
NG0211:3211: gnam thog chen po rang 'dod dbab //
NG0211:3212: sbyor ba'i rgyal po khong du gzhug / de nas
NG0211:3213: yang bcom ldan 'das kyis nyid kyi sku gsung thugs
NG0211:3214: rdo rje las drag sngags 'di bton to //
NG0211:3216: ram thun ro myag dz+wa la ram kham ram /
NG0211:3217: ram thun ma ra ya nr-i dza kham khyer lam ram /
NG0211:3218: rag thum ro myag khas rbad /
NG0211:3219: e yam kham ram trag chem srog la thun b+h+yo /
NG0211:3220: sarba tsit+ta sbur nan kham shag rbad b+h+yo /
NG0211:3221: dgra bo'i srog la hur thum nan 'drid rbad /
NG0211:3222: sarba sha trum hri myags rbad /
NG0211:3224: las 'di snang snang bya ba min //
NG0211:3225: thog ser skyin thang sbyor bar bshad //
NG0211:3226: de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis ltas ngan gyi sbyor ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0211:3227: sprel dang byi la wa thod dang *//
NG0211:3228: sbrul dang srin bya phag sha dang *//
NG0211:3229: gzugs dang ming rus bcas la bca' //
NG0211:3230: drag sngags khri bdun dug chu bsku //
NG0211:3231: tshes brgyad srod la mkhar la gzhug / gzugs rnams 'thab cing sgra 'byin du //
NG0211:3232: sbyor ba smin nas rten rnams gdon //
NG0211:3233: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis nyid kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje las drag sngags 'di bton to //
NG0211:3234: e dun ka yam ru sti nan du ting has phob /
NG0211:3235: las kyi rgyal po 'bru bzhi yis //
NG0211:3236: 'byung ba bzhi dkrug dwangs ma sdud //
NG0211:3237: ye shes bzhi yi thig le rdzogs //
NG0211:3239: kun gyi rtsa ba dril bar bshad //
NG0211:3240: dpal tshe bdag gi dgongs rgyud nag po las /
NG0211:3241: thog ser sbyor ba'i le'u ste nyi shu dgu pa'o
NG0211:3242: // // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis rgyud
NG0211:3243: kyi don 'khor la gdams pa 'di gsungs so //
NG0211:3244: rgyud ni 'brel pa gsum dang bcas //
NG0211:3247: yul sems gnyis 'dzin rang snang shugs //
NG0211:3248: blta spyod man ngag thabs cig dang *//
NG0211:3249: gzhi lam 'bras bu ro gcig gnas //
NG0211:3250: 'khor 'das snang srid don la gcig / bde dang sdug bsngal rgyu mthun 'das //
NG0211:3251: rang bzhin bdag nyid ngang du rdzogs //
NG0211:3252: bde ba nyams dang 'od gsal ro //
NG0211:3253: so ma lhug pa rdzogs te gnas //
NG0211:3254: thabs dang thabs gnyis thabs bsam yas //
NG0211:3255: bya ba med par rang shar 'di //
NG0211:3256: a dang yang dag sgyu mar sbyar //
NG0211:3257: e dang skye ba'i cho 'phrul rdzogs //
NG0211:3258: ma skyes skye ba gnas las 'das //
NG0211:3260: bde ba'i ye shes ro nyid mnyam //
NG0211:3261: rgyud kyi rgyal po 'dzin pa dang *//
NG0211:3262: mnyam pa'i don la drod len pa //
NG0211:3263: sangs rgyas nyid dang skal ba mnyam //
NG0211:3264: 'di la yun gyi don ldan pas //
NG0211:3265: che bas che ba'i yon tan rdzogs //
NG0211:3266: rang lus rdo rje sems dpa' med //
NG0211:3267: yan lag rdo rje stong bdag med //
NG0211:3268: stong pa nyid las gzhan med pas //
NG0211:3269: snying po don gyi sbyin pa yin //
NG0211:3270: sbyor dang sbyor ba rang bzhin pas //
NG0211:3271: rang nyams bde ba'i sbyor bar bshad //
NG0211:3272: 'di de bde dang smin pa'i mchog / zung du zungs mtshams kun spangs te //
NG0211:3273: yon tan ma lus kun ldan pa'i //
NG0211:3274: 'di la 'jig rten dngos grub mchog / ma lus 'byung phyir snying po'i don //
NG0211:3275: rgyal ba kun gyi thig le can //
NG0211:3277: bka' yi bstan pa ma lus kyi //
NG0211:3278: snying po mchog dang don zab pas //
NG0211:3279: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa dril ba yin //
NG0211:3280: nga yi sbyor ba me lce 'di //
NG0211:3281: khro tshogs gang gi stobs bsdus yin //
NG0211:3282: nga yi stobs kyi drag sngags 'di //
NG0211:3283: bgrod pa thob pa'i go mtshon mchog / nga yi gsang ba'i sgron ma 'di //
NG0211:3284: ma rig 'khar ba'i bde lam yin //
NG0211:3285: 'di la gnas shing bsgrub pa dang *//
NG0211:3286: 'dod pa'i dngos grub len pa dang *//
NG0211:3287: phyag rgya chen po rab sbyor ba //
NG0211:3288: 'bras bur nges pa'i thabs su bshad //
NG0211:3289: mnyam pa'i rgyal por rgyas par bsngags //
NG0211:3290: gsang ba'i bdag por legs gsungs pa'i //
NG0211:3291: nye bar gyur pa'i rgyud 'di la //
NG0211:3292: bgrod pa'i stobs kyis gang len pa //
NG0211:3293: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dzin //
NG0211:3294: rnal 'byor bde ba'i lam can la //
NG0211:3295: nga yang dam las mi g.yel bsrung *//
NG0211:3296: sangs rgyas kun gyis bsngags pa yin //
NG0211:3297: don gnyis mngon du spyod pa'i phyir //
NG0211:3298: tshad ma bzhi yis rab brtags pa'i //
NG0211:3300: rtsol dang bsgrub pa'i mtha' las 'das //
NG0211:3302: rgyu rkyen bgrod pa'i sar ma lhung *//
NG0211:3303: rdzas dang rtags la rten mi 'cha' //
NG0211:3304: mchod dang thugs dam bskang mi dgos //
NG0211:3305: thams cad ngo bo ma bcos pa /
NG0211:3306: kho na chos nyid gcig pa las //
NG0211:3307: lhun grub rang byung longs spyod sku //
NG0211:3308: las dang sbyor ba sna tshogs sprul //
NG0211:3309: sku gsung ma btsal bgrod thob med //
NG0211:3311: dag chos nyid rol pa'i rgya //
NG0211:3312: chos nyid rig pa rang byung dpal //
NG0211:3313: ye shes chen po rang gsal ba //
NG0211:3316: ngo bo mi dmigs gnyis kyis dben //
NG0211:3317: snang stong gnyis med ye shes sku //
NG0211:3318: 'dzin rtog mtha' gnyis rang bzhin med //
NG0211:3319: med pa'i ngang las snying po gnas //
NG0211:3320: sgyu ma lhun grub yul la rol //
NG0211:3321: 'khor ba ma spangs rang sar gsal //
NG0211:3322: gsal ba mtshan nyid lhun gyis grub //
NG0211:3323: 'di de bde dang smin pa'i las //
NG0211:3324: sangs rgyas gsung gi zab mo gnas //
NG0211:3325: che bas che ba'i yon tan ldan //
NG0211:3326: mos dbang spyod pa'i rnal 'byor rnams //
NG0211:3327: bgrod pa dbang gi phyag rgyar btab //
NG0211:3328: rig pa'i brda yis med cing bsnyad //
NG0211:3329: rdo rje stong bdag che bar gnas //
NG0211:3330: sems can sangs rgyas ma lus kun //
NG0211:3331: rgyud 'di bzung zhing bstan par bya //
NG0211:3332: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la 'khor thams cad rjes su yi rangs nas mngon par bstod do //
NG0211:3333: dpal tshe bdag gi dgongs rgyud nag po las /
NG0211:3334: rgyud gtad pa'i le'u ste sum cu pa'o // //
NG0211:3335: rgyud kyi snying po dam pa zhes bya ba sangs
NG0211:3336: rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa gcig tu bsdus pa
